org.eclipse.nvplayout.model

Class CalibrationBlock

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.nvplayout.model.CalibrationBlock

  • public class CalibrationBlock
extends java.lang.Object
    CalibrationBlock is the first layer of the model.
    This model contain the definition of a memory block, i-e :
    • Name of block.
    • The start address of the block.
    • The ID of the block.
    • The number of variable in the block.
    • The memory size of the block.
    • The reference of the different variable.

    Based on a MVC model

    Version:
    0.0 Alpha EarlyAccess Beta Tester
    Author:
    GLI feat Software Team
    See Also:
    CalibrationVariable
